  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Patient with relapsing remitting multiple sclerosis taking avonex are included in this double
      blind randomized control trial. Simvastatin is compared to placebo. end points of edss ,
      total attack, new enhancing lesion and newt2 lesion in mri is evaluated as end point.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
